channel.title: Enso Release | Happy xmas every1 :)
channel.description:
The reason why i'm releasing this is that I saw a leaked copy at r-s. Anyways, here it is! contains months of work. And has lots of fixes you could even say that it's more bug free than a 718.
[B][U]Credits[/U][/B] [I]Fuzenseth Milf hunter Dragonkk Cjay [/I]
[img]http://puu.sh/9H18G/80b1990e98.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/9H1bZ/7ac7cc560d.jpg[/img] [img]http://puu.sh/9H1gJ/ec100ec2e4.jpg[/img] Safe portal [img]http://puu.sh/9H0G8/8fef5c7df7.jpg[/img]
Team fights [img]http://puu.sh/9H0MN/4bf7193a82.jpg[/img]
Features *Quest System (shit af) *Appearence - fully done *DFS spec and such sagaies, elite voids , chinchompas *Area system *Plugin system *Many areas *Pickables all of them *RS2 full clan wars (team,safe,pvp) *Completed lunar spellbook (spec transfer etc and working accept aid) *random events *Achievements *Alch spells *NPC transformation (what i mean is ape atoll monkeys etc) *Ape Atoll dungeon with safe spots, camerashake rock falling and so on *Very good combat system, it's not same as in basic 667s *unique tele system *Slayer skill *Dungeoneering (shit af but started real way) *Ourania altar ... and LOTS, LOTS of more.
I've spent lots of time on this project and it is easily the most advanced 667/667 ever done.
If you're using, atleast thank the thread and be thankful of the all the work that i've done.
